    "description": "NSW Inc. operates as an enterprise, services, embedded, and device solutions provider in Japan. It provides business solutions, such as consulting, system design, development, maintenance, and operation solutions for manufacturing, distribution, finance, insurance, and government sectors. The company also offers IT services, including servers and networks designing; secure environment development; and operating and monitoring systems, as well as IoT & AI services. In addition, it is involved in the embedded system development business, which include development of applications, middleware, and drivers for automotive and industrial sectors; and edge device solutions. Further, it develops LSI and FPGA for image processing and communication control fields. The company was formerly known as Nippon Systemware Co., Ltd. and changed its name to NSW Inc. in June 2022. NSW Inc. was incorporated in 1966 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
